 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-156"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체를 포함할 수도 있습니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> 고 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> 규칙에 의미 체계 값 및 의미 체계 키를 추가 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-156">An <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object may also contain <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> objects that add semantic values and semantic keys to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-157">음성 인식 엔진은 구 인식 하는 경우 인식된 된 구와 뿐만 아니라는 의미 체계 정보를 반환 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-157">The speech recognition engine will return the semantic information, as well as the recognized phrase, when it recognizes the phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-158">참조 [의미 체계 해석 태그](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14)) 자세한 내용은 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-158">See [Semantic Interpretation Markup](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14)) for more information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-159">다음 예제에서는 라는 문구를 인식 하는 문법의 전 세계 월드컵 성공한에 국가 이름 뒤에 "가 전 세계 월드컵에 국가".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-159">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-160">만든 후 합니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 개체 `winnerRule` 문자열 식별자를 부여 하 고 `WorldCupWinner`, 예제에서는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> 문자열을 추가 하는 방법 "가 전 세계 월드컵에 국가" 규칙에 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-160">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-161">두 개의 추가 규칙을 만듭니다 `ruleEurope` 고 `ruleSAmerica`입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-161">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-162">다시 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> 메서드를 예제 추가 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체를 `WorldCupWinner` 규칙에 대 한 참조를 포함 하는 규칙 `ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-162">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-192">범위에 대 한 기본값은 `Private`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-192">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-193">만 개인 규칙을 포함 하는 문법의 루트 규칙 또는 루트 규칙에서 참조 되는 다른 규칙의 규칙 참조에 의해 인식에 대해 활성화할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-193">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-194">개인 규칙을 포함 하는 문법의 루트 규칙으로 선언 된 경우가 아니면 외부 문법 개인 규칙을 참조할 수 없습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-194">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-195">해당 범위 설정 된 경우 `Public`, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 에서 참조 하 여 인식에 대 한 개체를 활성화할 수는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> 또는 외부 문법의 규칙을 포함 하는 문법의 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-195">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-196">다음 예제에서는 라는 문구를 인식 하는 문법의 전 세계 월드컵 성공한에 국가 이름 뒤에 "가 전 세계 월드컵에 국가".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-196">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ed186-197">이라는 공용 규칙을 만들면 `WorldCupWinner` 공용 해당 규칙의 범위를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-197">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner` and sets the scope of that rule to Public.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope)), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica)})));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed186-198">만든된 문법에 다음과 같은 형식입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed186-198">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England< /item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```
